text: Hi! Wudsys are purple and gold. I know this for sure!
ok, are any of the others purple and gold?
So far I have seen no other creatures that are purple and gold. But they might exist. I think that in order to be a Wudsy, the creature has to be purple and gold, and also look like a bird or insect.
I think fish-like creatures are not wudsys ever, but I can't be sure because I've never seen a purple and gold fish.
